__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
This is a modified version of the Oak Ridge OpenSHMEM Benchmark Suite/ SSCA1 developed by Thomas Naughton, Ferrol Aderholdt, Matt Baker, Swaroop Pophale, Manjunath Gorentla Venkata and Neena Imam
It contains a mpi, gaspi and OpenSHMEM version. 

To compile:
* Set flags in script/path.sh and the adapat the machine file
* Choose between mpi, shmem and gaspi by changing the variable GASPI_MPI_SHMEM in script/path.sh
* navigate to script/
* bash build.sh

To run:
* navigate to script/
* bash run.sh
* in run.sh choose the number of ranks
